9,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:29:56.000Z","msg":"青衣行雷啦"},{"pid":"7e6c0c3d0026165b00b738c7f2fb8d0e237fb567","tid":1387911,"uid":267942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:30:07.000Z","msg":"沒有氣餒的本錢，必須加強文宣<br />\n<br />\n夢遊時要幫手提供安全撒離路線， 附近道路情況<br />\n<br />\n日落時間，<br />\n<br />\n尾班車時間， 尾班前60分鐘開始溫馨提示<br />\n<br />\n一定要至少留2條退走比自己走<br />\n<br />\n不受傷 不被補 一齊黎 一齊走"},{"pid":"7f7207367ef8cc00fb7993cf8db41d786536252f","tid":1387911,"uid":275468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:30:26.000Z","msg":"行雷<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d95e48abe86e203688a518ef58d4e766d286d8a","tid":1387911,"uid":31482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:30:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e9f35d506579cf9a602cbb070119f09394c2816","tid":1387911,"uid":56260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:30:44.000Z","msg":"留意天氣 小心行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e603c37ddc6fdb779a51fbd45ec9a4562a6d208","tid":1387911,"uid":205710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:31:17.000Z","msg":"就嚟落雨，大家小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8223d906c1ed9b1a71766e68cbfbcc6df5b4b7c","tid":1387911,"uid":208274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:31:59.000Z","msg":"行雷劈死班狗官"},{"pid":"6514d667b29b151a393c6a21515d798a50420aaa","tid":1387911,"uid":289694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:32:05.000Z","msg":"其實落雨先好，對班狗好不利"},{"pid":"23b0f4854da0b31280117293a1936840849b71c8","tid":1387911,"uid":56260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:32:20.000Z","msg":"可能突然好撚大雨<br />\n留意天氣 小心行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3e94ade14f2f393ce3dadb7c9178e0249168d3d","tid":1387911,"uid":267942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:32:42.000Z","msg":"沙田已暴雨"},{"pid":"e9137eba368a23c736bebbb6d650ae3980cce2e1","tid":1387911,"uid":56260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6514d667b29b151a393c6a21515d798a50420aaa","tid":1387911,"uid":289694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:32:05.000Z","msg":"其實落雨先好，對班狗好不利"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:33:02.000Z","msg":"自己都要提防 好多輕裝過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd6e5bec390fd69095bf3c6078a411fc1b798e81","tid":1387911,"uid":255934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:33:26.000Z","msg":"行雷中 大家小心"},{"pid":"eca6102cced319ef10f5983d3dfe14b7bddbe3a1","tid":1387911,"uid":15984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6514d667b29b151a393c6a21515d798a50420aaa","tid":1387911,"uid":289694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:32:05.000Z","msg":"其實落雨先好，對班狗好不利"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:33:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bae739a11ae59d5c480347948efc2a7eb6fea94","tid":1387911,"uid":86184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:34:27.000Z","msg":"葵芳落緊"},{"pid":"2ec924ced63d74fe661929452ea4a6f763e5feeb","tid":1387911,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:34:51.000Z","msg":"即刻落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8edc94b360aa1c6a7ac7c70701a1b1192cf47414","tid":1387911,"uid":151256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:34:59.000Z","msg":"大家去室內避雨 今晚完啦好嘛 聽朝東區法院見呀"},{